*** Settings ***
# Robot Framework test for @mcu_name@ running on Renode.
# Generated by Meson configure_file — do not edit.
#
# Run with:  renode-test @robot_path@
# Requires:  Renode >= 1.14 with Robot Framework support

Suite Setup       Setup
Suite Teardown    Teardown
Test Timeout      30s
Resource          ${RENODEKEYWORDS}

*** Variables ***
${RESC}    @resc_path@

*** Test Cases ***
@mcu_name@ Unit Tests
    [Documentation]    Run boost::ut unit tests on simulated @mcu_name@.
    ...    Output travels via ARM semihosting; exit code propagated via SYS_EXIT.
    Start Emulation
    Wait For Halt    timeout=15
    ${code}=    Execute Command    cpu PC
    # boost::ut calls std::exit(n_failures); semihosting forwards the code.
    # Renode sets the halt reason: 0x20026 = clean exit, 0x20023 = error exit.
    Should Contain    ${HALT_REASON}    ADP_Stopped_ApplicationExit

*** Keywords ***
Setup
    Execute Script    ${RESC}

Teardown
    Terminate And Log Results
